title: #063 - Behind-the-scenes of 1,000 New Clients
itunes:title: #063 - Behind-the-scenes of 1,000 New Clients
description:
Last week I launched my brand new membership site, Project Storyline, and it was a game-changer. My goal was to welcome in 800 new members, and we ended up welcoming in more than 1,000! It was an incredible accomplishment and experience, and in this episode I take you behind-the-scenes of what it was *really* like.

Recorded in the airport, as I was on my way to spend time with my Mastermind group in Necker Island, you hear me share openly about what went right, what went wrong, and what I’m pondering as I venture into this next chapter of my business.
